        <h2 class="fade title">About Samnivesha</h2>
        <p class="fade">
          Samnivesha is the annual technical fest of the Department of Civil and
          Environmental Engineering, organised by ACE, IIT Patna. It was
          initiated in the year 2019 with a thought of redefining the image of
          what Civil Engineering meant to us. It is a technical extravaganza
          conducted to testify the hard work and teamwork of the young minds to
          showcase their skills through wide-ranging events and get their
          efforts rewarded. This fest aims to bring experts of the industries,
          students, prominent professors together and update the future
          seedlings about the development and enhancement in the field of Civil
          Engineering.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 content-div">
        <h2 class="fade title">About ACE</h2>
        <p class="fade">
          Association of Civil Engineers (ACE) is the technical club of the
          Department of Civil and Environmental Engineering, IIT Patna. With the
          aim to provide exposure outside regular classroom teaching, we develop
          a strong platform promoting student-faculty interaction outside of the
          world of regular academics. With this, we aim to form a forum where
          people can share their knowledge and experience, a forum that passes
          on the baton through the years so that it provides a head start to
          students entering the department to maximize their time by taking
          forward successes and learning from mistakes.
        </p>
